'''''Kill and Kill Again''''' ni film y'ibikorwa yo mu 1981 iyobowe na Ivan Hall. Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo James Ryan nka Steve Chase wahawe akazi ko gukiza umuhanga Horatio Kane, washimuswe n'umuhanga Marduk. Chase akoranya itsinda ryabacanshuro basanga inzira igana ku gihome cy'umugome hanyuma ugasanga barwanira ubuzima bwabo uko bafashwe.

''Kill and Kill Again'' ni urukurikirane rwa film ''[[:en:Kill_or_Be_Killed_(1980_film)|Kill or Be Killed]]'' kandi yatangiye gufatwa amashusho muri kamena 1980. Iyi filime yafatiwe mu [[Burayi]] no muri [[Amerika]] hamwe n'abakinnyi ahanini bakomoka muri [[Afurika]] y'Epfo. Yasohotse i New York ku ya 8 Gicurasi 1981. Yakiriye ibitekerezo bibi byatanzwe na ''Variety'' na ''The New York Times'' basanze filime "idashimishije" kandi ifite "umugambi mubi".

== Kurekura ==
''Kill and Kill Again'' yasohotse i New York ku ya 8 Gicurasi 1981.  Ku ya 12 Kanama 1980, ''Umunyamakuru wa Hollywood'' yatangaje ko hateganijwe filime ya gatatu muri uruhererekane.  Kugeza mu Kuboza 2013, nta filime ikurikirana yagiye mu bikorwa.
